<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">س ك ف:</span> <span class="c2">(الْإِسْكَافُ)</span> وَاحِدُ <span class="c2">(الْأَسَاكِفَةِ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(الْأُسْكُوفُ)</span> لُغَةٌ فِيهِ.<span class="c5"> وَقَوْلُ مَنْ قَالَ:</span> كُلُّ صَانِعٍ عِنْدَ الْعَرَبِ إِسْكَافٌ فَغَيْرُ مَعْرُوفٍ.<span class="c5"> وَقَوْلُ الشَّمَّاخِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَشُعْبَتَا مَيْسٍ بَرَاهَا إِسْكَافْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">إِنَّمَا عَلَى التَّوَهُّمِ كَمَا قَالَ آخَرُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلَمْ تَذُقْ مِنَ الْبُقُولِ فُسْتُقَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَ <span class="c2">(أُسْكُفَّةُ)</span> الْبَابِ عَتَبَتُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>